LangTools 0.1.0

 0. Requirements
 ---------------
 The following software should be installed prior to   
  - PHP 5 or later (downloadable at http://php.net/)


 1. Install
 ----------
 In order to use langTools, either :
  a. download the latest release from http://blog.fbollon.net/lang_tools  
  > tar xvfj lang_tools_x.x.x.tar.bz2
  
  b. export the latest nightly build from http://svn.fbollon.net/lang_tools
  > svn export http://svn.fbollon.net/lang_tools/trunk/ lang_tools

  
 2. Usage
 --------
 Executable scripts are located in the '[rootFolder]/scripts' directory:
  a. langTools.php : main script
  
  See doc/usage.txt for usage recommandations 
  
 3. Contribute
 -------------
 Please report bugs and enhancements at http://trac.fbollon.net/lang_tools


